origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "Insurance.compare_coverage",
        "description": "比较不同保险产品的覆盖范围，返回比较结果。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "comparison",
                "description": "不同保险产品覆盖范围的比较结果。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.term_life_coverage",
        "description": "获取定期寿险的覆盖范围信息。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "coverage",
                "description": "定期寿险的覆盖范围详情。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.whole_life_coverage",
        "description": "获取终身寿险的覆盖范围信息。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "coverage",
                "description": "终身寿险的覆盖范围详情。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.recommend_based_on_family_responsibility",
        "description": "根据家庭责任推荐合适的保险产品。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "family_responsibility",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "描述家庭责任的字符串。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "recommendation",
                "description": "基于家庭责任的保险产品推荐。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.calculate_premium",
        "description": "根据用户输入的参数计算保险产品的保费。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "age",
                "type": "INTEGER",
                "description": "用户的年龄。"
            },
            {
                "name": "coverage_amount",
                "type": "FLOAT",
                "description": "所需的保险覆盖金额。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "additional_benefits",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "额外的保险福利选项。"
            }
        ],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "premium",
                "description": "计算出的保费金额。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.check_claim_status",
        "description": "查询特定保险索赔的状态。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "claim_id",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "索赔的唯一标识符。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "status",
                "description": "索赔的当前状态。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.get_policy_details",
        "description": "获取特定保险政策的详细信息。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "policy_id",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "保险政策的唯一标识符。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "policy_details",
                "description": "保险政策的详细信息。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.estimate_future_value",
        "description": "根据当前保单信息估算未来价值。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "policy_id",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "保险政策的唯一标识符。"
            },
            {
                "name": "years",
                "type": "INTEGER",
                "description": "估算的年数。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "future_value",
                "description": "估算的未来价值。"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
